### JACHACKS ITS Challenge — API REST Client
### Requires: VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@now = {{$timestamp}}
@oneDayAgo = {{$timestamp - 86400}}

# ─── Ping ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ping

# ─── Devices ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all access points (ordered by building, then name)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/devices

# ─── History ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get site-wide client history — last 24 hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history

### Get site-wide client history — custom time range (epoch seconds)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?from=1744300000&to=1744400000

### Get per-AP client history — last 24 hours
# Replace ap_id with a real UUID from GET /api/devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?ap_id=4866e21e-d83a-3eb5-9c9f-ee55fe2644de

### Get per-AP client history — custom time range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history?ap_id=4866e21e-d83a-3eb5-9c9f-ee55fe2644de&from=1744300000&to=1744400000

# ─── Heatmap ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get current AP occupancy (latest snapshot per AP + coordinates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/heatmap/current
